---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Briefs Conventions | AI Coachella Valley">
  <section class="card">
    <h1>Briefs Conventions</h1>
    <p>Use this format when drafting or reviewing signals for publication.</p>

    <h2>Required fields</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>title</code> (clear, specific, factual)</li>
      <li><code>date</code> (YYYY-MM-DD)</li>
      <li><code>summary</code> (one concise sentence)</li>
      <li><code>sources</code> (at least one URL)</li>
      <li><code>signal_type</code> (e.g. <code>adoption</code>)</li>
      <li><code>confidence</code> (low, medium, high)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Recommended fields</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>city</code></li>
      <li><code>sector</code></li>
      <li><code>time</code></li>
      <li><code>tags</code></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Example</h2>
    <pre><code>{`---
title: "Regional operator launches AI pilot"
date: 2026-02-19
city: "Palm Desert"
sector: "Retail"
signal_type: adoption
confidence: medium
sources:
  - https://example.com/source
summary: "A verified pilot launch indicates practical AI adoption in local operations."
---

The organization launched a bounded pilot with measurable operational scope.

Source: https://example.com/source
`}</code></pre>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #d8dbe1;
    padding: 1rem;
    max-width: 56rem;
  }

  pre {
    background: #f7f9fc;
    border: 1px solid #d8dbe1;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.8rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
</style>
